                "Added support for Apache ActiveMQ Artemis STOMP protocol Added support for the ActiveMQ Artemis open-source message broker through the Simple Text Oriented Messaging Protocol (STOMP). It delivers a reliable and scalable messaging system, offering flexibility for STOMP-based integrations. See Apache ActiveMQ Artemis in the Commerce Configuration Guide."
